      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must have documented V&V test suite with regression testing and configuration management at Gradation 4 for MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Commercial CFD solver has documented QA procedures and regression test suite, but configuration management and change control documentation fall short of Gradation 4 requirements. Independent code review not completed."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
