      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence and round-off error must be characterized for hemolysis transport equations at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence of hemolysis scalar transport equations was not systematically evaluated. Residual tolerances were set by default solver settings without verification that hemolysis QoI is insensitive to further tightening. This factor was not assessed and represents an unresolved epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
