    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the VAD hemolysis CFD model at MRL 5 has been reviewed. Seven factors were assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels. Six factors remain not assessed. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification provides sufficient confidence in the hemolysis predictions for regulatory submission. The model is accepted for the intended use.",
